  "remarks": "TAi.020 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Director, Kabul Custom House under the Taliban regime. Works on recruitment for the Taliban movement as of mid-2013. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Popalzai tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 Feb. 2001 (amended on 3 Sep. 2003, 21 Sep. 2007, 3 Oct. 2008, 29 Nov. 2010 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
